sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/CI
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant MutatingWH as Mutating Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS
    participant ValidatingWH as Validating Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS
    participant RayClusterCtrl as RayCluster Controller
    participant CertMgr as cert-manager API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant HeadPod as Ray Head Pod<br/>6379, 8265, 10001/TCP
    participant Workers as Ray Workers
    participant GCS as Ray GCS Server<br/>6379/TCP Redis
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Ingress/Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant Serve as Ray Serve<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus

    Note over User,GCS: Flow 1: RayCluster Creation

    User->>K8sAPI: POST RayCluster CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>MutatingWH: Admission request<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    MutatingWH-->>K8sAPI: Mutated RayCluster<br/>(defaults, security configs)
    K8sAPI->>ValidatingWH: Validation request<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    ValidatingWH-->>K8sAPI: Validation approved
    K8sAPI-->>User: RayCluster created

    RayClusterCtrl->>K8sAPI: Watch RayCluster CR<br/>Bearer Token (SA)
    RayClusterCtrl->>CertMgr: Request TLS certificates<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    CertMgr-->>RayClusterCtrl: Certificates created
    RayClusterCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Head Pod + Service<br/>Bearer Token (SA)
    RayClusterCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Worker Pods<br/>Bearer Token (SA)
    K8sAPI-->>HeadPod: Deploy Ray Head
    K8sAPI-->>Workers: Deploy Ray Workers

    Workers->>GCS: Register with GCS<br/>Optional mTLS
    GCS-->>Workers: Registration confirmed

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 2: RayJob Submission

    User->>K8sAPI: POST RayJob CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>User: RayJob created

    RayClusterCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create RayCluster for job<br/>Bearer Token (SA)
    K8sAPI-->>HeadPod: Deploy cluster

    RayClusterCtrl->>HeadPod: Submit job via gRPC<br/>10001/TCP Optional mTLS
    HeadPod->>GCS: Job metadata<br/>6379/TCP Optional mTLS
    HeadPod->>Workers: Execute job tasks<br/>Ray Protocol Optional mTLS
    Workers-->>HeadPod: Task results
    HeadPod-->>RayClusterCtrl: Job completed

    Note over Client,Prometheus: Flow 3: RayService Model Serving

    Client->>Gateway: POST /predict<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.3<br/>Optional Bearer Token
    Gateway->>Serve: Forward request<br/>8000/TCP HTTP<br/>Optional TLS
    Serve->>Workers: Inference request<br/>Ray Protocol Optional mTLS
    Workers-->>Serve: Prediction result
    Serve-->>Gateway: HTTP response
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON response

    RayClusterCtrl->>K8sAPI: Monitor service health<br/>Bearer Token (SA)
    K8sAPI-->>RayClusterCtrl: Service status

    Note over Prometheus,RayClusterCtrl: Flow 4: Metrics Collection

    Prometheus->>RayClusterCtrl: GET /metrics<br/>8080/TCP HTTP<br/>No auth
    RayClusterCtrl-->>Prometheus: Prometheus metrics<br/>(reconciliation, errors)
